{"title":"狠狠地打","authors":["萧三"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":9,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"狠狠地打\t萧三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打！打！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狠狠地打！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来一下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打一下！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你再来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我再打！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“U—2”，“幽”一二，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听了刺耳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打，打这小偷！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打，打这飞贼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋匪帮说，它失踪了……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像是，一去渺茫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬  却不打自招："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有情报　归他存档。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们呀，你还不信？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬　侵略成性。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么你　心迷了窍？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和虎狼　大讲交情！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“和平队”——大批特务，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"专门干　破坏颠覆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们呀，你还幻想？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们呀，别再糊涂！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人　经验痛苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到现在　就不信邪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是敌是友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分的清楚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不受欺骗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕威吓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁来侵犯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一定打！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打！打！狠狠地打！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把一切惯贼匪盗痛打！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打！打！打！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把美国佬彻底打垮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"9月14日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}